[FILE:92:descriptions/desc.primary]
openmpt123 is a cross-platform command-line based module file player that 
uses libopenmpt.


[FILE:197:descriptions/desc.library]
libopenmpt is a cross-plattform C++ and C library to decode tracked music 
files (modules) into raw PCM audio stream. It is based on the player code 
of the OpenMPT (Open ModPlug Tracker) project.


